title: Star Trek: Prelude to Axnar (2014)
description: The film is presented as an episode of a Federation documentary pertaining to the Four Years War with the Klingon Empire, narrated by noted historian John Gill and featuring interviews of actual participants on both sides. It begins on Stardate 2241.03, two decades before the original series, and recounts the initial victories by the Klingons, who did not see the Federation as a worthy adversary. The losses result in a change in Starfleet leadership and the creation of the Ares class cruisers, Starfleet's first warships, to counter the Klingon D6 battlecruiser
